config.markdown:
# Sample data
---
This dashboard shows field extraction and sample views. 
Read the doc inside the pack to onboard your windows data

search.query:
|lookup EventID on EventID|summarize count()
  by strcat(EventID," : ", description)

dataset="$vt_lookups" lookupFile="windows_sample"
 | extend _time=now()-rand(300), _raw=sample
 | project _time, _raw
 | render event
 | extract @'<(?<_KEY_0>[\w]+)(\s[\w=\"]+)?>(?<_VALUE_0>[^<]*)<\/\1>'
 | extract @'<Data Name="(?<_NAME_1>\w+)">(?<_VALUE_1>[^<]+)'
